channel.title: Need some help
channel.description:
Hi. I'm planning on making my first Project Infinity server, and I wonder... How can I change the current Gameframe, interface and icons etc, to the old runescape (2004-2005) interface, gameframe, icons, etc?
Would be happy if you could give me a link to a tutorial or help me personally ^^
here's a pic of how it was in 2004: [url=http://media.photobucket.com/image/runescape%202004%20interface/erlem2000/runescape3.jpg]http://media.photobucket.com/image/runescape%202004%20interface/erlem2000/runescape3.jpg[/url]
